    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, but the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may require some upcoming maintenance to bring it back to its best. It's an honest car at an honest price for someone who values utility over aesthetics.",
