      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a premier balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure mechanical reliability and aesthetic consistency. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, the vehicle delivers a confident and composed driving experience. It represents an excellent opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber automobile that has been treated with consistent care. Professional inspections are welcomed to confirm the integrity of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 31500.0,
